 <a href="https://youtu.be/pj0E-gGiJ6M" target="_blank">
  The Life and Times of Timuel D. Black: A Centenary Symposium
 </a>
</p>
<p>
 For more about Prof. Timuel D. Black, our great South Side civil rights activist and historian, please visit our
 <a href="http://civicknowledge.uchicago.edu/media.shtml">
  Media Page
 </a>
 , our
 <a href="http://civicknowledge.uchicago.edu/mlk-initiative.shtml">
  Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Initiative
 </a>
 page, and the page devoted to the
 <a href="http://civicknowledge.uchicago.edu/garden.shtml">
  Timuel D. Black Edible Arts Garden
 </a>
 . For more about the CKP's support for the Timuel D. Black Centenary Weekend, celebrating Prof. Black's 100th Birthday, please
 <a href="/files/Timuel_D_Black_100_Years_of_Music_and_M.pdf" target="_blank">
  click here
 </a>
 .
</p>
